OL,3,CUK competition watchdog launches Oasis
OL,4,Cticket sale investigation
OL,6,FThe UK competition watchdog has
OL,7,Flaunched an investigation into
OL,8,FTicketmaster over Oasis concert ticket
OL,9,Fsales, it has announced, including how
OL,10,F"dynamic pricing" was used.
OL,12,FThe Competition and Markets Authority
OL,13,F(CMA) said its investigation would
OL,14,Flook into whether the ticket seller
OL,15,Fbreached consumer protection law.
OL,17,FIt will also look into if people were
OL,18,Fgiven clear and timely information to
OL,19,Fexplain the "dynamic" pricing and if
OL,20,Fconsumers were put under time pressure
OL,21,Fto buy at a higher price.
