OL,6,FThe CMA said it would now engage with
OL,7,FTicketmaster and gather evidence from
OL,8,Fvarious other sources, which may
OL,9,Finclude the band's management and
OL,10,Fevent organisers.
OL,12,FIt added, it should not be assumed
OL,13,Fthat Ticketmaster had broken consumer
OL,14,Fprotection law.
OL,16,FCMA chief executive Sarah Cardell
OL,17,Fsaid: "It's important that fans are
OL,18,Ftreated fairly when they buy tickets,
OL,19,Fwhich is why we've launched this
OL,20,Finvestigation.
