OL,6,F"It's clear that many people felt they
OL,7,Fhad a bad experience and were
OL,8,Fsurprised by the price of their
OL,9,Ftickets at checkout.
OL,11,F"We want to hear from fans who went
OL,12,Fthrough the process and may have
OL,13,Fencountered issues so that we can
OL,14,Finvestigate whether existing consumer
OL,15,Fprotection law has been breached.
