OL,6,F"The CMA also welcomes the
OL,7,FGovernment's recent announcement that
OL,8,Fit will consult on measures to provide
OL,9,Fstronger protections to consumers in
OL,10,Fthe ticketing sector, wherever they
OL,11,Fbuy their tickets.
OL,13,F"This has been a priority focus for
OL,14,Fthe CMA for several years, having
OL,15,Fpreviously taken enforcement action
OL,16,Fand recommended changes to improve the
OL,17,Fsecondary tickets market.
