OL,3,CUK competition watchdog launches Oasis
OL,4,Cticket sale investigation
OL,6,F"We are committed to working closely
OL,7,Fwith Government to tackle the
OL,8,Flongstanding challenges in the ticket
OL,9,Fmarket."
OL,11,FThe statement comes days after many
OL,12,Ffans were shocked by standard tickets
OL,13,Ffor the band's reunion tour more than
OL,14,Fdoubling.
OL,16,FIt prompted the Government and the CMA
OL,17,Fto pledge they will look into the use
OL,18,Fof dynamic pricing.
