OL,6,FMeanwhile, others were left angry and
OL,7,Fdisappointed after being left empty-
OL,8,Fhanded, having waited in an online
OL,9,Fqueue for hours to buy tickets.
OL,11,FOn Wednesday, Oasis announced new
OL,12,FWembley Stadium dates using a new
OL,13,Fticketing plan following the chaos
OL,14,Fover the weekend.
OL,16,FLiam and Noel Gallagher have extended
OL,17,Ftheir Live '25 tour to include two
OL,18,Fmore London shows in September.
